<HL>
   LEISURE &amp; ARTS -- The Mobile Guide:
   Europe's Cultural Capital
   ----
   By Isabel Fonseca
</HL>
<DATE>
04/30/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A12
</SO>
<CO>
   EUROP
